Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:00.65,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 說你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:28.68,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,工口松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.23,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,松崎 生理上厭惡松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.98,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來看不是抖M松嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.48,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.88,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到課桌和鞋櫃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.35,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有收到巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.07,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:21.74,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:43.35,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我抽屜裡有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:57.36,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,笛子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.88,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,照橋同學 喜歡寵物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:39.17,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}註：日語中「幹（架）」和「買（東西）」用的動詞相同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.02,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,那片真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:39.01,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我是力 燃堂力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.68,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺放不下這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:42.30,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心裡 我們已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:44.39,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不會和你說話了
